thread.title_full: Otticanet recensione scritta da Anha Tran

author: Anha Tran
title: Anha Tran
text:
I have been ordered my sunglasses at Otticanet since 2009. They have a huge amount of selected products to choose from. Price is very competitive and super fast shipping. They are absolutely US Import Tax Free. Sometimes I got the Fedex Import Tax Bills. I contacted Otticanett and they refunded back this money and ask me just go ahead and paid the bill. They refunded the import tax back.
I love their service and very trusted company to buy sunglasses from. Thanks a lot.
